Description: Resizable window with 4:3 aspect ratio preservation
 Adds a letterbox/pillarbox viewport so that the fixed 1024x768 logical
 coordinate system is always rendered centered with correct proportions,
 regardless of window size. Black borders fill the unused areas.
 .
 SDL_WINDOWEVENT_SIZE_CHANGED is handled to update the viewport whenever
 the user resizes the window. RestoreViewport() replaces direct
 glViewport(0,0,ScreenWidth,ScreenHeight) calls so all scene code
 benefits automatically via Mode2D().
